<p>
  The adding students via spreadsheet feature is designed to allow teachers and admins to add many students or make
  many changes at one time.
</p>
<p>
  The first step is to create a valid spreadsheet. The simplest way to do this is to simply click the 'Download class
  spreadsheet' button, found at the top of the edit
  page. You could also click here:
</p>
