<p>
  You can now edit the file to make certain changes to the class:
<ul>
  <li>
    To create a new student and add them to the class,
    fill out their information in a new row and leave the Octopi student number column blank.
  </li>
  <li>
    To add an existing student to a class, fill in their information just like existing students.
    All that is required to do this is their Octopi student number, but you will be asked to confirm you are adding the correct
    student if you
    do not supply the rest of their information.
  </li>
  <li>
    To change the password of a student already in the class, fill out their password and password confirmation columns
    with the
    password you want them to have.
  </li>
</ul>
</p>
