<p>
  Once you are have saved your changes, return to the edit class page and click 'Choose File'. A folder browser will
  open and you can navigate to the spreadsheet you want to use. You can also click and drag a file over the 'Choose
  File' button. Supported file types include Microsoft Excel (.xls, .xlsx), ODF spreadsheet (.ods), and Text CVS (.csv).
  Next click 'Submit' and you will be brought to a page that shows you all the changes that will be made.
  If you notice anything incorrect, you have the option to cancel.
</p>
<p>
  <b>Remember:</b> Every student within the same school must have a different login name.
</p>
